title: Beautiful 3 bed / 1.5 bath apartment available September 1s

Green lake Way N., Seattle, WA 98103', 'Beautiful 3 bed / 1.5 bath apartment available September 1st in Green Lake', 'Open house on Tuesday, August 9 at 6:00 p.m.', 'Rent is $3,650 per month.', 'Available to move in September 1st.', 'Requires 1-year lease.', 'Credit score > 675 and no prior evictions is required', 'No more than 3 occupants', 'Location: 5744 E. Green lake Way N., Seattle, WA 98103', 'House Features:', 'This completely renovated contemporary apartment has amazing', 'unobstructed views of Green Lake.', 'Many restaurants, shops,', 'grocery stores, and a public library are within walking distance.', '•Three spacious bedrooms', '• One and one-half bathrooms', '• Brazilian cherry hardwood floors', '• Granite countertops', '• Stainless steel appliances', '• Full size washer/dryer', '• Reserved off-street parking', '• Cable ready', '• Large deck overlooking the lake', '• Lots of natural light', '• No pets', '• Secure extra storage available', 'Location', '• Easy access to both I-5 and WA-99.', '• Great public transit options within walking distance.', '• 1 block from Green Lake golf course', '• Walking distance to heart of dozens of restaurants, bars, and shops.', '• 10 minute drive to downtown and South Lake Union.', '• Jog or walk around the lake or rent a kayak/paddle boat.']
